snippet.title: Cooking Mama: Cookstar Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
If you can’t stand the heat, get into Mama’s kitchen! Cooking Mama is back with her most fantastic and fun video game adventure ever! 
Introducing Cooking Mama: Cookstar. A brand-new Cooking Mama experience created specifically for Nintendo Switch™.

Order Cooking Mama: Cookstar here:

Amazon: https://bit.ly/cookstarmama
Walmart: https://bit.ly/cookstarwalmart

Follow us here:

Twitter: https://twitter.com/cookstarmama
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/cookstarmama
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/cookingmamacookstar/
